---
// src/components/Footer.astro
---
<footer class="bg-white border-t border-slate-200 py-8 mt-12">
    <div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-lg">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-rocket text-xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="font-bold text-xl tracking-tight text-slate-900">AI方舟</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">探索AI的诺亚方舟，收录1400+全品类AI工具，助你高效工作。</p>
                <div class="flex space-x-4">
                    <a href="#" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-blue-600 transition">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-weixin text-xl"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-blue-600 transition">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-github text-xl"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-blue-600 transition">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-twitter text-xl"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">分类导航</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">AI 对话</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">AI 绘画</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">AI 写作</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">AI 编程</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">全部分类</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">关于我们</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">关于AI方舟</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">提交AI工具</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">联系方式</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">隐私政策</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">用户协议</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">订阅更新</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">获取最新AI工具和行业资讯</p>
                <div class="flex">
                    <label for="subscribe-email" class="sr-only">邮箱地址</label>
                    <input type="email" id="subscribe-email" placeholder="你的邮箱地址" class="flex-1 px-3 py-2 border border-slate-200 rounded-l-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-500 text-sm">
                    <button id="subscribe-btn" class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-r-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition text-sm">
                        订阅
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-slate-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4 md:mb-0">© 2025 AI方舟(AIArk) 保留所有权利</p>
            <div class="flex space-x-6 text-sm text-slate-500">
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">隐私政策</a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">用户协议</a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">免责声明</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
